{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_08_01",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――VENUSプログラムランキング五位との",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ライブバトル終了後",
      "startTime": 2.6733331442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、勝ったで！\nうちら、トップ5に勝ったんや！",
      "startTime": 6.6524135583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.0116323868
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、ほんまに頑張ったんよ\n新曲作りもギリギリまで粘ってこだわって……",
      "startTime": 13.1999999206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けも、瑠依ちゃんに頼らないフォーメーションを\nみんなで考えて、毎日動けなくなるまで練習して……",
      "startTime": 20.8333332539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.0468928415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんまに……ほんまに頑張ったんよ……\n努力が報われるって、こんなに嬉しいものなんや",
      "startTime": 30.9999999206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5664623339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それは優が本気で頑張ったからさ\n頑張った分だけ、報われた時の喜びは増すんだ",
      "startTime": 38.3999999206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "今までのライブバトルは、勝てそうな相手ばかりで\n心のどこかで余裕があったんやろうなぁ",
      "startTime": 46.0333332539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.2531290768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "せやからこんなに必死になって\nギリギリまで自分を追い込んだりしなかった……",
      "startTime": 51.7333332539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "持てる力を出し尽くして勝つことが、こんなに大変で\nこんなに嬉しいことやったなんて……",
      "startTime": 59.9666665872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.6678002752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "これも{user}さんのおかげです\n悩んでたすみれちゃんの相談に乗ってくれたんやろ？",
      "startTime": 65.8333332539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "そのおかげで、うちらは挑戦する気持ちを取り戻せた\n……大切なことを思い出させてくれて、ありがとう",
      "startTime": 74.6666665872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.872914449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺はほんの少し手を貸しただけだ。挑戦すると\n決めたのも、勝つために努力したのも、優自身だ",
      "startTime": 82.5170673121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "おめでとう、優。よく頑張ったな\nこれは紛れもなく、トリエル三人の勝利だ",
      "startTime": 90.8666793029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.5047511495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに\nそう言ってもらえるのが一番嬉しいわ……",
      "startTime": 95.5184071567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.1314171549
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "100連勝したご褒美も用意してあるから\n楽しみにしててくれ",
      "startTime": 101.7333454609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.5447505073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ほんまに？　{user}さんからの\nご褒美ってなんやろ、楽しみやわぁ",
      "startTime": 106.3666787942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その後、しばらくして",
      "startTime": 111.4180838979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.9180884755
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.9180884755
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "優、トリエルの三人で行った\n山形の温泉はどうだった？",
      "startTime": 115.8666787942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが\n予約してくれた温泉旅館が、ほんまに最高やったわ",
      "startTime": 119.2333454609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9085919137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "うちの顔を見て下さい\n美肌の湯のおかげで、ゆで卵みたいにぷるぷるや",
      "startTime": 126.4333454609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "うちのぷるぷるの肌、触り心地抜群やで\nほっぺた、触ってみます？",
      "startTime": 135.7666787942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.8852589999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え、遠慮しておくよ",
      "startTime": 138.8852589999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……\nほんまに最高のご褒美やったわ",
      "startTime": 143.0333413919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんやすみれちゃんと一緒にお風呂に入って\n一緒にお鍋を食べて、一緒に寝れるなんて……",
      "startTime": 149.7666747253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.2783158376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "さすが{user}さん\nうちの喜ぶツボを分かってくれてはるなぁ",
      "startTime": 156.2666747253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.7283158376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "みんなにリフレッシュしてほしかっただけで\nそれ以上の意味はなかったんだけどな",
      "startTime": 162.3859489231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで、優\n実は温泉に関係することで、もう一つ話があるんだ",
      "startTime": 166.5682976295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.2421253278
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.2421253278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！　うちに写真集のオファー！？",
      "startTime": 173.2921253278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.3254586612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。「アイドルとデートしている気分を\n味わえる写真集」というコンセプトで……",
      "startTime": 180.5151790941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "優の地元である京都で、プライベート感のある\n素の表情を撮りたいそうだ",
      "startTime": 186.8199231076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.0799150539
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "いい話やと思いますけど……\nそれと温泉になんの関係があるんですか？",
      "startTime": 191.7666747253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
